<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[439, 136, 562, 150]]<|/det|>
1. ALGEBRA 

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[81, 167, 244, 181]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation 

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[118, 197, 388, 213]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^2 + bx + c = 0\), 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[417, 215, 585, 250]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b \pm \sqrt{b^2 - 4ac}}{2a}\]

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[81, 274, 231, 287]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[246, 295, 753, 330]]<|/det|>
\[(a+b)^n = a^n + \binom{n}{1}a^{n-1}b + \binom{n}{2}a^{n-2}b^2 + \ldots + \binom{n}{r}a^{n-r}b^r + \ldots + b^n\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[118, 348, 500, 382]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n-r)!r!}\) 

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[81, 413, 384, 427]]<|/det|>
Arithmetic series 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[248, 413, 390, 430]]<|/det|>
\[u_n = a + (n-1)d\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[248, 437, 536, 464]]<|/det|>
\[S_n = \frac{1}{2}n(a+l) = \frac{1}{2}n\{2a+(n-1)d\}\]

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[81, 490, 230, 503]]<|/det|>
Geometric series 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[248, 488, 384, 505]]<|/det|>
\[u_n = ar^{n-1}\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[248, 512, 431, 545]]<|/det|>
\[S_n = \frac{a(1-r^n)}{1-r} \quad (r \neq 1)\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[248, 549, 420, 575]]<|/det|>
\[S_\infty = \frac{a}{1-r} \quad (|r| < 1)\]

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[402, 614, 597, 627]]<|/det|>
2. TRIGONOMETRY 

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[81, 645, 160, 659]]<|/det|>
Identities 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[415, 674, 583, 722]]<|/det|>
\[\begin{align*}
\sin^2 A + \cos^2 A &= 1 \\
\sec^2 A &= 1 + \tan^2 A \\
\cosec^2 A &= 1 + \cot^2 A
\end{align*}\]

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[81, 770, 246, 783]]<|/det|>
Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\) 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[405, 794, 592, 825]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C}\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[405, 830, 595, 847]]<|/det|>
\[a^2 = b^2 + c^2 - 2bc \cos A\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[443, 855, 558, 881]]<|/det|>
\[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc \sin A\]<｜end▁of▁sentence｜>
